front.title: •Jedi Mind Trick (V)
front.gametext: USED: If opponent just initiated a battle or Force drain, they must use 2 Force, or it is canceled.  LOST: If your Jedi in battle (unless with a Dark Jedi, Hutt, or Toydarian), 'wave had at' (add or subtract 2 from) an opponent's just drawn destiny.
front.lore: 'You will bring Captain Solo and the Wookiee to me.'
